2.1 Data

d <- readMat("KruschkeData.mat")

y <- as.numeric(d$y)
nstim <- as.numeric(d$nstim)
nsubj <- as.numeric(d$nsubj)
n <- as.numeric(d$n)
t <- n*nsubj
a <- as.numeric(d$a)
d1 <- d$d1
d2 <- d$d2

2.2 MCMC

data <- list("y", "nstim", "t", "a", "d1", "d2")

# parameters to be monitored:
parameters <- c("c", "w", "predy")

# model
model_text <- "
# Generalized Context Model
model{
  # Decision Data
  for (i in 1:nstim){
    y[i] ~ dbin(r[i],t)
    predy[i] ~ dbin(r[i],t)
  }  
  # Decision Probabilities
  for (i in 1:nstim){
    r[i] <- sum(numerator[i,])/sum(denominator[i,])
    for (j in 1:nstim){
      tmp1[i,j,1] <- b*s[i,j]
      tmp1[i,j,2] <- 0
      tmp2[i,j,1] <- 0
      tmp2[i,j,2] <- (1-b)*s[i,j]
      numerator[i,j] <- tmp1[i,j,a[j]]
      denominator[i,j] <- tmp1[i,j,a[j]] + tmp2[i,j,a[j]]
    }
  }  
  # Similarities
  for (i in 1:nstim){
    for (j in 1:nstim){
      s[i,j] <- exp(-c*(w*d1[i,j]+(1-w)*d2[i,j]))
    }
  }
  # Priors
  c  ~ dunif(0,5)
  w  ~ dbeta(1,1)
  b <- 0.5 
}
"
samples <- jags(data, parameters.to.save = parameters, 
                model.file = textConnection(model_text), 
                n.chains=1, n.iter=5000, n.burnin=2000, n.thin=1)

bayesplot::mcmc_scatter(as.mcmc(samples), pars = c("c", "w"), 
             size = 1.5, alpha = 0.1) +
  scale_x_continuous(breaks = seq(0, 5, by = 1), limits=c(0,5)) +
  scale_y_continuous(breaks = seq(0, 1, by = 0.2), limits=c(0,1)) +
  labs(x = "Generalization (c)", y = "Attention Weight (w)") +
  theme_bw(base_size = 18) +
  theme(panel.grid.major = element_blank(), 
        panel.grid.minor = element_blank())

posterior(samples) %>% 
  select(starts_with("predy")) %>% 
  pivot_longer(cols = everything(), names_to = "Stimulus", values_to = "Decision") %>% 
  separate_wider_delim(cols = "Stimulus", delim = ".", names = c(NA, "Stimulus")) %>% 
  mutate(Decision = Decision/t) %>% 
  ggplot(aes(y = Decision, x = Stimulus)) +
  ggdist::stat_eye() +
  scale_y_continuous(breaks = seq(0, 1, by = 0.2), limits=c(0,1)) +
  geom_line(data = data.frame(Stimulus = seq(1,8), Decision = y/t), 
            aes(x = Stimulus, y = Decision)) +
  theme_bw(base_size = 18) +
  theme(panel.grid.major = element_blank(),
